{"tid":2145501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全國人大常委會今開幕　議程新增香港立法會真空期問題","createTime":"2020-08-08T05:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T06:15:29.000Z","uid":285559,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"129d1471e3179caf3ef6dac35c40b044fcbae4fb","tid":2145501,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"十三屆全國人大常委會第二十一次會議，於周六至下周二（8日至11日）在北京舉行，周六早上在人民大會堂開幕。消息指，會議議程中新增包括處理香港立法會換屆選舉延遲一年出現「真空期」問題的事項。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會法工委周五（7日）公布，今次會議亦將審議城市維護建設稅法草案、契稅法草案、預防未成年人犯罪法修訂草案、動物防疫法修訂草案、著作權法修正案草案等。<br />\n<br />\nsource: on.99"},{"pid":"dc2926217fd831d1f84153c73806371bb6aba5d2","tid":2145501,"uid":100697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"who fucking care"},{"pid":"cab98605d6571d6603dcdfb7cb3f4896cf29e009","tid":2145501,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"由人大委任"},{"pid":"b8970bc3bb332b6448540cb9df459caec4525d18","tid":2145501,"uid":5787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:50:02.000Z","msg":"成日開會<br />\n班死老野咁得閒入去坐同拍手<br />\n早d死左佢喇"},{"pid":"7360f599db13ffa0eac52595b65d507d7899e577","tid":2145501,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"沒有，沒有，沒有<br />\n通過"},{"pid":"3ad7dd6b6ab33a4da7f12c68f1218783d0f58660","tid":2145501,"uid":183509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"順手搞埋d bno 國籍問題唔該各位大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}